BOOKS OPEN THIS WEEKEND for Dallas, Richmond, and Los Angeles! This booking round is for October-December. 
Dallas bookings start Saturday at noon CST and on Sunday at noon CST for new clients! Monday I’ll be opening my books for @animeink_con in Richmond on October 20th-22nd, and for my guest spot at @lostboysdtla on October 31st-November 2nd.
